Chicken Jockey Clicker: A cheerful clicker with speedy chickens

Chicken Jockey Clicker is a super entertaining clicker game where gamers join unique chicken races. Your mission is to train, upgrade, and boost your racing chicken to become quicker and stronger to win the competition.

This is not just a simple mouse-clicking game – it’s a journey of progress, where you see your little chicken gradually grow into a true champion on the racetrack. Try it today and make your chicken the speed champion!

Gamer’s mission

Click to speed up

  • Keep clicking to move your chicken forward and pass your rivals.
  • The faster you click, the better your chance of victory.

Train and upgrade your chicken

  • Use the rewards collected after each race to improve speed, strength, and sprint ability.
  • With upgrades, you can handle more challenging tracks with ease.

How to control

Use the mouse to play.
